Window Attribute Tags
=====================

Usage: OpenWindowTagList_/Windowtags

WA_DetailPen: ( ti_Tag=$80000068 )

Specify the DetailPen for Intuition to use
in rendering details in the window titlebar
such as gadgets and text, in ti_Data.


Window Attribute Tags
=====================

Usage: OpenWindowTagList_/Windowtags

WA_BlockPen: ( ti_Tag=$80000069 )

Specify the BlockPen for Intuition to use
